05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-cannot-accept-hamas-demand-to-end-war-gallant-rafah-offensive-imminent/0000018f-491b-d91a-a5af-e9ffa33f0000</guid></item><item><title>《周六夜现场》回避学生抗议，选择与家长轻松取笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/snl-sidesteps-student-protests-and-opts-for-lighthearted-fun-at-their-parents/0000018f-48e1-d17f-adcf-f9e318340000</link><description>该短剧以脱口秀圆桌会议为特色，主持人询问家长对抗议活动的感受</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/snl-sidesteps-student-protests-and-opts-for-lighthearted-fun-at-their-parents/0000018f-48e1-d17f-adcf-f9e318340000</guid></item><item><title>他们小时候逃离了纳粹。现在他们因为真主党而无法回家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-escaped-the-nazis-as-children-they-are-still-not-home-because-of-hamas/0000018f-484f-d6c3-afdf-4d5f3b520000</link><description>过去七个月里，数十名从黎巴嫩边境附近什洛米撤离的以色列人，包括约 20 名大屠杀幸存者，一直住在耶路撒冷的一家酒店里</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 13:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-escaped-the-nazis-as-children-they-are-still-not-home-because-of-hamas/0000018f-484f-d6c3-afdf-4d5f3b520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列纪念大屠杀之际，“生者游行”在欧洲开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/march-of-the-living-set-to-begin-in-europe-as-israel-commemorates-the-holocaust/0000018f-484a-d6c3-afdf-4d5b5b700000</link><description>从奥斯威辛到比克瑙的无声游行，以及穿越布达佩斯的游行，“生者游行”标志着二战结束时几个月内超过 55 万匈牙利犹太人被杀害。在以色列，10 月 7 日之后的大屠杀纪念日将呈现不同的面貌</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 12:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/march-of-the-living-set-to-begin-in-europe-as-israel-commemorates-the-holocaust/0000018f-484a-d6c3-afdf-4d5b5b700000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡希望哈马斯拒绝停火提议。如果没有，他就转向破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hoped-hamas-would-reject-israels-offer-when-it-didnt-he-turned-to-sabotage/0000018f-4817-d414-a5bf-fb37db290000</link><description>以色列刑事被告总理更专注于拯救无能的极右翼政府，而不是拯救被困在加沙七个月的人质，他正在竭尽全力破坏以色列将人质带回家的最后也是最好的机会</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 11:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hoped-hamas-would-reject-israels-offer-when-it-didnt-he-turned-to-sabotage/0000018f-4817-d414-a5bf-fb37db290000</guid></item><item><title>照片：耶路撒冷另一种火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-photos-a-different-kind-of-fire-in-jerusalem/0000018f-4814-d516-afbf-fed6e4cc0000</link><description>“圣火”仪式已经举行了一千多年。这就是上周在耶路撒冷庆祝的方式</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 11:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-photos-a-different-kind-of-fire-in-jerusalem/0000018f-4814-d516-afbf-fed6e4cc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡内阁一致投票决定关闭以色列半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/israeli-government-votes-unanimously-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018f-4841-d91a-a5af-e9f5c8de0000</link><description>以色列通讯部长称赞这一决定“结束了该网络运转良好的煽动机器”；以色列警方突袭该频道耶路撒冷办事处并没收设备；半岛电视台猛烈抨击这一决定，称其为“诽谤性和欺骗性的举动”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 11:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/israeli-government-votes-unanimously-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018f-4841-d91a-a5af-e9f5c8de0000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙示威到关闭以色列馆：威尼斯双年展上政治掩盖了艺术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/politics-overshadows-art-at-the-venice-biennale/0000018f-33ac-d0b5-a59f-33ed816d0000</link><description>“一个暂停的国家和一个暂停的展览”：以色列艺术家露丝·帕蒂尔对于关闭她的国家馆并不后悔。与此同时，政治抗议活动正在蔓延到威尼斯军械库以外的地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 09:12:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/politics-overshadows-art-at-the-venice-biennale/0000018f-33ac-d0b5-a59f-33ed816d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在美国校园援引反犹太主义，国际刑事法院在大屠杀日仪式上发出逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-mark-holocaust-remembrance-day-beginning-sunday-evening-at-yad-vashem/0000018f-4762-d91a-a5af-e7f725290000</link><description>以色列大屠杀纪念日是一个国家纪念日，每年都会以两分钟的警报和默哀来纪念，以色列各地也会举行仪式和活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 08:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-mark-holocaust-remembrance-day-beginning-sunday-evening-at-yad-vashem/0000018f-4762-d91a-a5af-e7f725290000</guid></item><item><title>报告发现 2023 年西方反犹太主义事件大幅增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/antisemitic-incidents-in-the-west-saw-massive-spike-in-2023-report-finds/0000018f-47d6-d91a-a5af-e7f7a6800000</link><description>反诽谤联盟和特拉维夫大学的一份联合报告发现，“世界上发生了自二战结束以来最严重的反犹太主义事件浪潮”，并且在 10 月 7 日之后，“仇恨海啸”向世界各地的犹太人释放</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 08:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/antisemitic-incidents-in-the-west-saw-massive-spike-in-2023-report-finds/0000018f-47d6-d91a-a5af-e7f7a6800000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，西岸整个地区的巴勒斯坦社区已被清空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-war-began-entire-areas-of-the-west-bank-have-been-emptied-of-their-communities/0000018f-39a9-d9c3-abcf-7bfd66980000</link><description>10 月 7 日，约旦河西岸的定居者暴力达到了顶峰：自此，18 个巴勒斯坦牧民社区被迫背井离乡，居民现在住在其他村庄郊区的临时住所里，一贫如洗，对未来感到焦虑</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 07:15:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-war-began-entire-areas-of-the-west-bank-have-been-emptied-of-their-communities/0000018f-39a9-d9c3-abcf-7bfd66980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列即将与哈马斯达成协议，但没有制定加沙战略计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-nearing-a-deal-with-hamas-with-no-strategic-plan-for-the-day-after-in-gaza/0000018f-457e-d17f-adcf-fdff77cd0000</link><description>以色列尚未准备好休战期间和休战后加沙的管理计划，而且没有政府能够满足返回北方的巴勒斯坦人的需求，哈马斯、巴勒斯坦权力机构或以色列军队是否会管理民政事务的问题迫在眉睫</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-nearing-a-deal-with-hamas-with-no-strategic-plan-for-the-day-after-in-gaza/0000018f-457e-d17f-adcf-fdff77cd0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府官员表示，加沙停火协议对于与真主党达成协议至关重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-deal-critical-to-reaching-agreement-with-hezbollah-u-s-officials-say/0000018f-456b-d91a-a5af-e5ff895f0000</link><description>美国官员告诉停火谈判中的同行，一旦达成结束加沙战斗的协议，以色列、真主党和黎巴嫩政府之间将有可能迅速达成协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 03:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-deal-critical-to-reaching-agreement-with-hezbollah-u-s-officials-say/0000018f-456b-d91a-a5af-e5ff895f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：以色列-加沙过境点在拉法的迫击炮弹袭击中三名士兵丧生，九人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israel-will-not-agree-to-end-the-war-as-part-of-gaza-deal-with-hamas/0000018f-468d-d17f-adcf-ffef8ee60000</link><description>哈马斯表示回应加沙休战提议，重申人质交易的起点是结束战争 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列不会屈服于哈马斯结束战争的要求 ■ 加沙的以色列国防部长：拉法攻势迫在眉睫 ■ 中央情报局局长前往“卡塔尔举行“紧急”会议，官员称加沙停火谈判濒临“崩溃” ■ 以色列国防军称，从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 40 枚火箭弹，造成两人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 02:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israel-will-not-agree-to-end-the-war-as-part-of-gaza-deal-with-hamas/0000018f-468d-d17f-adcf-ffef8ee60000</guid></item><item><title>据报道加沙谈判取得进展，数万名以色列人抗议人质和停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-rally-for-hostage-deal-against-netanyahu-govt-amid-reports-of-emerging-truce/0000018f-43f5-d17f-adcf-fbf7bd0f0000</link><description>周六的抗议活动在以色列各大城市举行，参加人数异常之多。抗议者还要求提前举行选举。在耶路撒冷的一次集会上，以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的父亲表示：政客们必须记住，我们正在为真正的人民而战</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 17:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-rally-for-hostage-deal-against-netanyahu-govt-amid-reports-of-emerging-truce/0000018f-43f5-d17f-adcf-fbf7bd0f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>